  <div class="timeline">
    <div class="tl-item">
      <span class="tl-date">2018 – 2021</span>
      <h3>MPhil in Mathematics</h3>
      <div class="tl-org">Capital University of Science &amp; Technology (CUST), Islamabad · CGPA 3.40/4.00</div>
      <p>Thesis: <em>Generalized Signcryption Based on Elliptic Curve Cryptography</em> — extending an ECC-based signcryption scheme so it can also run in signature-only or encryption-only mode, with full security-attribute and computational-cost analysis.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item">
      <span class="tl-date">2015 – 2017</span>
      <h3>MSc in Mathematics</h3>
      <div class="tl-org">COMSATS University Islamabad, Attock Campus</div>
      <p>Thesis: <em>Flow of Eyring-Powell Fluid in a Channel Using Adomian Decomposition Method</em> — a series solution for non-Newtonian channel flow, with a parametric study of velocity, flow rate, and stream function.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="tl-item">
      <span class="tl-date">2012 – 2014</span>
      <h3>BSc in Mathematics</h3>
      <div class="tl-org">Horizon Degree &amp; Commerce College, Chakwal</div>
      <p>Core coursework: Calculus, Linear Algebra, Mathematical Methods, Metric Spaces, Mechanics.</p>
    </div>
